identifications.body: Female, ID based on yellow markings all the way down the dorsal surface of the abdomen, including S10, in conjunction with no lateral thoracic markings, long hind legs, greenish eyes and a relatively small head. Also the capital "I" bordered by oval spots on the upper surface of the thorax is discernible in this image.
